title: Clint Black -- Spend My Time: Piano/Vocal/Chords
description: Spend My Time is a reflective album which shows how Clint Black has matured since his record-breaking debut in 1989. Our matching folio includes four pages of black and white photos. Titles: The Boogie Man * Everything I Need * Haywire * Just Like You and Me * A Lover's Clown * A Mind To * My Imagination * She's Leavin' * Someone Else's Tears * Spend My Time * We All Fall Down * What Ever Happened.
author: Clint Black
